{"tid":2346010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"10港人判刑在即 林鄭袖手至今","createTime":"2020-12-30T03:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T05:01:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1446deb8334793e6f289ac8000da3cf4d8da52c2","tid":2346010,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/4AL4U7D65BD43NMP2L6DU3FMBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2F4AL4U7D65BD43NMP2L6DU3FMBA%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=bab06efa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2F4AL4U7D65BD43NMP2L6DU3FMBA%2F&h=36fbcefa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/4AL4U7D65BD43NMP2L6DU3FMBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n10港人判刑在即 林鄭袖手至今<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JTjN21hAXRtKs-xXQnUhTU1KmDs=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ABELQBVOMBA2RG3TV2J3YVGPWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJTjN21hAXRtKs-xXQnUhTU1KmDs%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FABELQBVOMBA2RG3TV2J3YVGPWM.jpg&h=b9b08185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■12港人家屬及關注組上月在吉澳放氣球，冀將思念寄往被扣對岸鹽田的家人。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年8月，12名港人懷疑在偷渡台灣途中，被內地海警截獲，以偷越邊境等罪名拘押，跌入了深不見底的中國司法黑洞。四個多月以來，家屬律師連一面都見不到當事人，更有人遭官方逼退。其中10人本周一（28日）開庭，法院稱有「被告人家屬」參與，今早判刑。家屬批評當局拖延宣判欠理據。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：流亡抗爭 不似預期  鄭文傑：拍門搵政要無回音<br />\n<br />\n今年8月，最先通報消息的是中國海警在26日發出的微博，指海上查獲12名涉嫌非法越境的人員。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n六國領事代表旁聽被拒<br />\n<br />\n在香港，特區政府角色被動，特首林鄭月娥強調要尊重內地司法管轄權。傳媒更一度揭發政府飛行服務隊，涉嫌在事發當日「監察」12港人被捕的過程。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n事件得到國際迴響，美國國務卿蓬佩奧對事件表示深切關注，。。。。。。。。。。。。。包括英國、美國、葡萄牙等六國領事代表到現場試圖參與旁聽，但最終都被拒絕入內。"},{"pid":"4fff0d693f167fcc1cbc3258e40d432e48c72379","tid":2346010,"uid":323468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"宣傳大灣區有幾好都無用。"},{"pid":"e2a98234a3d5ad10ffecdf5fb6dd65dd6a0de53e","tid":2346010,"uid":35205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭藍屍黑狗LOGIC:&nbsp;抵你死啦"},{"pid":"f8e4632c753c5b7f3cf2ff4c6f1fa4a6c085539d","tid":2346010,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"乜嘢袖手旁觀啊<br />\n<br />\n人哋有份搵國安同飛行服務隊<br />\n親自將12個餸中架"},{"pid":"4b7043fbb933d0090429870ee1269a5e68bc4d51","tid":2346010,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜嘢袖手旁觀啊<br />\n<br />\n人哋有份搵國安同飛行服務隊<br />\n親自將12個送中架</blockquote>"},{"pid":"70350c1a71e6a19846d2e8fd4d7542cb09801916","tid":2346010,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢袖手旁觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夾埋曱甴同飛曱甴一齊設局送中啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9429dc395b69ee890381d934dd24121d38f7ddf3","tid":2346010,"uid":297152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"柒婆只愛雜種"},{"pid":"b8bde4ef85370df5bb2f7c52f62dca5014dfba48","tid":2346010,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0955004f46f1565f1ed3d856ae8c702f1e6ecb93","tid":2346010,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"偷渡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20a044bf760ee852ea806f9